title: Optional contents of compacts
context: ยง350C-5 Optional contents of compacts. A compact entered into pursuant to this chapter may: (1) Establish procedures and entitlements to medical, developmental, child care, or other social services for the child in accordance with applicable laws; (2) Contain other provisions as may be appropriate or incidental to the proper administration of the compact.
